  discoveryCards:
  - cardID: Level1_Nibbles
    unlockPlayerPrefsKey: Reward_Level1_Nibbles
    cardButton: {fileID: 2066380215}
    cardImage: {fileID: 352129527}
    characterEmoticonImage: {fileID: 1301873452}
    cardTitleText: {fileID: 2056123445}
    lockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cc5526266cd54904185f0361702a0f39, type: 3}
    unlockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c1014f79e4863da4ca6c8264a6ac60b9, type: 3}
    lockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 131c67e9b517b174dbbe06c6384008be, type: 3}
    unlockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 80467ffdade282d48943976b9c33b9c6, type: 3}
    openedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d0c296230777c6346a77c1f8e3b44119, type: 3}
    openedCardBackSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 828cb9fca7fb6fe45ab36f31aaefde61, type: 3}
    openedCardTitle: Nibbles
    openedCardTitleKey: NIBBLES
    openedCardFrontDescription: "<b>Character:</b> Nibbles\n<b>Represents:</b> Brasilodon
      Quadrangularis\n<b>Era:</b> Late Triassic\n<b>Time:</b> about 225 million years
      ago\n<b>Status:</b> Extinct\n<b>Size:</b> roughly 20 cm long\n\n<b>Focus:</b>
      \nFossil reconstruction, skeleton assembly, and early mammal anatomy."
    openedCardFrontDescriptionKey: REWARD_NIBBLES_FRONT
    openedCardBackDescription: "In this mission, you learned the names of important
      bones and bone structures by rebuilding parts of Nibbles\u2019 skeleton.\r\n\r\n<b>Cranium
      / Skull</b> \u2014 protects the brain and shapes the head.\r\n<b>Scapula /
      Shoulder blade</b> \u2014 connects the front limb to the body.\r\n<b>Humerus
      / Upper arm bone</b> \u2014 helps the front limb move and support weight.\r\n<b>Pelvis
      / Hip structure</b> \u2014 connects the body to the hind limbs.\r\n<b>Femur
      / Thigh bone</b> \u2014 supports the body and helps with movement.\r\n<b>Astragalos
      / Ankle bone</b> \u2014 helps transfer weight through the foot."
    openedCardBackDescriptionKey: REWARD_NIBBLES_BACK
    blankAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f408db3e7dbfc8944820254d0731c923, type: 3}
    earnedAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2cfe36d530ead2d47af5dc2430f4d480, type: 3}
    backBoneIconsGroup: {fileID: 0}
    rank: 0
    unlocksSideCharacter: 1
  - cardID: Level5_Yeti
    unlockPlayerPrefsKey: Reward_Level5_Yeti
    cardButton: {fileID: 651477651}
    cardImage: {fileID: 1720835273}
    characterEmoticonImage: {fileID: 2012603589}
    cardTitleText: {fileID: 1055350255}
    lockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cc5526266cd54904185f0361702a0f39, type: 3}
    unlockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c1014f79e4863da4ca6c8264a6ac60b9, type: 3}
    lockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3f03406fec19aeb4c92887acfb2dce46, type: 3}
    unlockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dac9b53c56f6e0249a861bbd7d5a27c7, type: 3}
    openedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: eb865a870dc366b4fb6a80bc4bb6468e, type: 3}
    openedCardBackSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 828cb9fca7fb6fe45ab36f31aaefde61, type: 3}
    openedCardTitle: Yeti
    openedCardTitleKey: YETI
    openedCardFrontDescription: "<b>Character:</b> Yeti\n<b>Represents:</b> Australopithecus\n<b>Era:</b>
      Pliocene to early Pleistocene\n<b>Time:</b> about 4.4 to 1.4 million years
      ago\n<b>Status:</b> Extinct\n<b>Size:</b> 1 to 1.5 meters tall\n\n<b>Focus:</b>
      \nBone function, balance, and movement."
    openedCardFrontDescriptionKey: REWARD_YETI_FRONT
    openedCardBackDescription: "In this mission, you matched each bone or structure
      by its function. Bones are not only shapes \u2014 they help bodies move, balance,
      and stand.\r\n\r\n<b>Cranium</b> \u2014 protects the brain and supports the
      senses.\r\n<b>Scapula</b> \u2014 helps position the shoulder and guide arm
      movement.\r\n<b>Humerus</b> \u2014 supports reaching, lifting, and front-limb
      movement.\r\n<b>Pelvis</b> \u2014 supports upright posture and connects the
      trunk to the legs.\r\n<b>Femur</b> \u2014 carries body weight during standing
      and walking.\r\n<b>Astragalos</b> \u2014 helps balance the body and guide smooth
      ankle motion."
    openedCardBackDescriptionKey: REWARD_YETI_BACK
    blankAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f408db3e7dbfc8944820254d0731c923, type: 3}
    earnedAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2cfe36d530ead2d47af5dc2430f4d480, type: 3}
    backBoneIconsGroup: {fileID: 0}
    rank: 0
    unlocksSideCharacter: 1
  - cardID: Level9_Achilles
    unlockPlayerPrefsKey: Reward_Level9_Achilles
    cardButton: {fileID: 1466565099}
    cardImage: {fileID: 1152932603}
    characterEmoticonImage: {fileID: 1046610683}
    cardTitleText: {fileID: 1261445565}
    lockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cc5526266cd54904185f0361702a0f39, type: 3}
    unlockedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c1014f79e4863da4ca6c8264a6ac60b9, type: 3}
    lockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f3a85df3b9ab0a5419b9835194cce05e, type: 3}
    unlockedCharacterEmoticonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ef93799e4bc9d584cb3315739c970454, type: 3}
    openedCardSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d3f8c21dda420e84086a2b29647e4819, type: 3}
    openedCardBackSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 828cb9fca7fb6fe45ab36f31aaefde61, type: 3}
    openedCardTitle: ACHILLES
    openedCardTitleKey: ACHILLES
    openedCardFrontDescription: "<b>Character:</b> Achilles\n<b>Represents:</b> Homo
      sapiens\n<b>Era:</b> Ancient Greece / Spartan era\n<b>Time:</b> about 2500
      years ago\n<b>Status:</b> Living species\n<b>Size:</b> around 1.7 meters tall\n\n<b>Focus:</b>
      \nHuman bone structures, archaeology, and cultural meaning."
    openedCardFrontDescriptionKey: REWARD_ACHILLES_FRONT
    openedCardBackDescription: "In this mission, you decoded bone amulets by observing
      their shape and meaning. In archaeology, bones can become objects of memory,
      identity, belief, and culture.\r\n\r\n<b>Cranium amulet</b> \u2014 can symbolize
      identity, thought, memory, or ancestry.\r\n<b>Scapula amulet</b> \u2014 can
      suggest protection, strength, or movement.\r\n<b>Humerus amulet</b> \u2014
      can represent action, work, or human ability.\r\n<b>Pelvis amulet</b> \u2014
      can symbolize support, life, posture, or origin.\r\n<b>Femur amulet</b> \u2014
      can represent strength, travel, or endurance.\r\n<b>Astragalos amulet</b> \u2014
      can symbolize balance, movement, luck, or play."
    openedCardBackDescriptionKey: REWARD_ACHILLES_BACK
    blankAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f408db3e7dbfc8944820254d0731c923, type: 3}
    earnedAstragalosBadgeSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2cfe36d530ead2d47af5dc2430f4d480, type: 3}
    backBoneIconsGroup: {fileID: 0}
    rank: 0
    unlocksSideCharacter: 1
